<font color="ffffff" size=5> 
<h2><b> About Me </b></h2>
</font>
<font color="ffffff" size = 4>
<p> I'm currently a research analyst at the Federal Reserve Bank of New York. I graduated from the University of Notre Dame in 2015 with a bachelor's degree in finance and economics.
</p>
<p> One of my personal hobbies is following bitcoin and distributed ledger technology more generally. If you're new to bitcoin, it might be worth checking out some of the info at <a href="https://bitcoin.org/en/">bitcoin.org</a>.</p>

<p>Here are links to some of my favorite cryptocurrency sites:</p>
